<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
  
    <hr>
  
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "FullSizeRender.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%" 
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>A student at the Two Rivers campus taking the Code to Success program. 
        I want to be an astrophysicist or a competer programmer/designer. The university
        that I wish to attend is the University of Utah, and graduate with none or little student debt.
        I want to travel the world before I turn 30, and hopefully have children and be happily married.</p>
        
        <p>
          <button 
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
          
          <button 
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>
        
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Ogden Pizzeria
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 2
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Rocky Mountain Junior High
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Fremont High School
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Junior college: Weber State University
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Dream University: University of Utah
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>  
  </div>
</div>



